title: Stunning executive home in highly coveted Bella Vista... 3 Beds
posting_body: ['78613 - Welcome to this absolutely gorgeous executive home in highly coveted bella vista offers 3 bedroom with in suite bathrooms and a half bathroom.', 'Great curb appeal upon driving up!', 'A dedicated office and formal dining greet you as you enter the foyer.', 'Gorgeous one story with a mother in law plan, a stone fireplace opens to the remodeled kitchen and a large game room opens to the living room.', 'The kitchen features designer tile backsplash, granite countertops, a gas stove and an extra-large center island.', 'Primary bedroom provides plenty of privacy and an attached fully remodeled in-suite spa-like bathroom featuring dual vanities, a walk-in frameless shower, and a soaking tub! .', 'A private fenced-in backyard provides plenty of space to entertain with an oversized covered patio and smart home sprinkler system.', 'Bella vista includes a pool complex, playgrounds and green areas.', 'Rarely do these come up for lease with this caliber of upgrades and character!', 'This home features beautiful hand scraped hardwood floors, smart home features (kitchen & patio lights, garage and ac), ceiling fans and there are a lot of windows for tons of natural light that make this a bright and happy home!', 'This location is an excellent location within a short drive to downtown austin.', 'Feeds into the award winning leander isd and cedar park hs!', 'You will be just minutes from shopping at lakeline and easy access to the toll roads, new apple campus, domain, lake travis, volente water park, chuys, torchys & tons of yummy restaurants!', 'What an amazing place to call home!', 'Available august 15th!!!!!!.', 'text or call now Daniel, Realtor at Team Price', 'show contact info']
